| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0403 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3f849878-a7f5-5cdc-9719-f20aa895fa0e"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
